---
<Layout title="Full Disclosure">
  <Container>
    <div class="">
        <Sectionhead>
            <Fragment slot="title">Full Disclosure</Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">Updated February 2, 2025
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">At Forever Viral Media, we believe in being fully transparent with our audience. This Full Disclosure page outlines important information regarding the services we provide, any affiliations, and how we may benefit from your interactions with our website or services. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.</p>

              <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">1. Affiliate Links</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">Some of the links on our website or in our content may be affiliate links. This means that if you click on these links and make a purchase, we may receive a commission or compensation at no additional cost to you. This helps support the ongoing operation of our website and services.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">We only recommend products and services that we believe may provide value to our users. However, please note that our recommendations are based on our own research, experiences, and judgment.</p>
          
              <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">2. Sponsored Content</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">Occasionally, we may feature sponsored content or promotions on our website. These are partnerships with brands or businesses that compensate us for promoting their products or services. Sponsored content will always be clearly labeled as such.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">Even with sponsored content, we aim to provide honest and unbiased information based on our experiences and insights.</p>
          
              <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">3. No Guarantee of Earnings</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">While we share strategies, tips, and resources that may help you improve your marketing efforts or business performance, we make no guarantees regarding your success. Individual results may vary based on your effort, skills, and external factors.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">We do not guarantee that using the services, products, or training offered on our website will result in financial success, and we strongly encourage you to conduct your own research before making any investments.</p>
          
              <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">4. Testimonials and Case Studies</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">We may share testimonials, case studies, or success stories from clients or users of our services. These are based on real experiences, but it’s important to understand that these results may not be typical and are not indicative of what you may achieve.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">Any testimonials or case studies shared on our website are meant to illustrate examples of what’s possible with the right effort and strategies but are not meant to promise specific outcomes or results.</p>
          
              <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">5. Third-Party Products and Services</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">We may reference or recommend third-party products, services, or websites. However, we are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or availability of third-party sites. Any interaction or transaction you have with a third-party provider is solely between you and the third party.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">We encourage you to read the terms and privacy policies of any third-party websites before engaging with them.</p>
          
              <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">6. Use of Cookies</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">Our website may use cookies to enhance your experience and analyze website traffic. Cookies help us understand how you interact with our website, which allows us to improve the content and functionality of the site. By using our website, you consent to our use of cookies as described in our <a href="[Insert Privacy Policy Link]" class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
          
              <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">7. Changes to This Disclosure</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">We may update this Full Disclosure page periodically to reflect changes in our practices or policies. When we do, we will post the updated version on this page with the new effective date. We encourage you to review this page periodically for any updates.</p>
          
              <h2 class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">If you have any questions or concerns about this Full Disclosure or the practices described on our website, please contact us at:</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 p-4">
              
                  <li>Email: foreverviralmedia@gmail.com</li>
                  <li>Phone: 216-296-7707</li>
                  <li>398 W Bagley Rd, Berea OH</li>
              </ul>
            </Fragment>
        <p>
            
